sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Memory
    participant SumLLM as "Summarizer LLM"

    User->>Memory: Turn 1: Hi I am Alice, a doctor in Paris
    Memory->>SumLLM: Summarize: new message added
    SumLLM->>Memory: Summary: Alice is a doctor in Paris.

    User->>Memory: Turn 2: I have 3 kids and love sushi
    Memory->>SumLLM: Update summary with new info
    SumLLM->>Memory: Summary: Alice is a doctor in Paris. She has 3 kids and loves sushi.

    User->>Memory: Turn 3: What do I do for work?
    Memory->>User: Injects summary into prompt
    Note right of Memory: LLM sees: Summary: Alice is a doctor...